---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_AUTHOR, SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={`研究框架 | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
    <style>
      .intro { padding: 3rem 0 1rem; max-width: 860px; }
      .intro p { color: rgb(var(--gray)); font-size: 1.14rem; }
      .weight-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem; }
      .weight { padding: 1.1rem; }
      .weight strong { display: block; font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0.25rem 0; }
      .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin: 1rem 0 2rem; }
      .card { padding: 1.25rem; }
      .card h2, .card h3 { margin-top: 0; }
      @media (max-width: 820px) { .weight-grid, .two-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <section class="intro">
        <span class="pill pill-red">由 {SITE_AUTHOR} 维护</span>
        <h1>A股股票中短线研究框架</h1>
        <p>这个站点记录A股个股研究、盘中修正、次日复盘和观察队列。目标是把题材强度、成交额、换手、日内位置、关键价位和仓位动作放进同一套可复盘流程。</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>当前评分权重</h2>
        <div class="weight-grid">
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill pill-red">题材</span><strong>25%</strong><p>主线强度与产业链扩散，代表资金方向。</p></div>
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill">强度</span><strong>20%</strong><p>涨幅、日内位置、突破关键位的力度。</p></div>
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill">成交</span><strong>20%</strong><p>成交额、量能放大和大单承接。</p></div>
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill">换手</span><strong>15%</strong><p>适度换手提升活跃度，高换手滞涨提高风险。</p></div>
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill">价位</span><strong>10%</strong><p>开盘价、日内高低点、前高、支撑压力。</p></div>
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill pill-amber">风险</span><strong>10%</strong><p>估值、连续加速、冲高回落、题材退潮。</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="two-col">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>四类股票</h2>
          <h3>主线龙头</h3>
          <p>题材最强、成交活跃、日内位置高，适合作为观察队列核心。</p>
          <h3>链条扩散</h3>
          <p>同题材补涨或中军品种，适合回踩低吸和分批做T。</p>
          <h3>修复跟踪</h3>
          <p>强势题材里位置较低或刚修复的品种，等待突破确认。</p>
          <h3>风险观察</h3>
          <p>下跌、冲高回落、高换手滞涨、跌破关键位的品种。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h2>复盘方法</h2>
          <ol>
            <li>记录观察队列 Top 5。</li>
            <li>收盘后更新实际涨跌幅、成交额和换手。</li>
            <li>对比龙头、中军、补涨、弱票的强弱变化。</li>
            <li>检查题材扩散、资金背离、高位过热和低位补涨。</li>
            <li>更新下一轮关键价位和持仓动作。</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="notice">
        <strong>每日同步约定</strong>
        <p>盘面截图、实时快照和收盘复盘进入正式结论后，同步写入博客；首页“当前观察队列”跟随最新交易窗口更新。A股行情主用腾讯快照和东方财富补充，港股与市场状态使用 moomoo/Futu OpenD，只读执行。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="notice">
        <strong>免责声明</strong>
        <p>本站内容为 {SITE_AUTHOR} 的个人研究记录，用于复盘股票研究框架和交易纪律，不构成投资建议。</p>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
